This place is awesome.  It's a small, old school Italian neighborhood grocery and deli. I'm 100% Italian and have dual citizenship with Italy so I like to think that my opinion is credible, but if you need further proof... Today I took my grumpy 86 year old father here.  He didn't want to go...I twisted his arm.  He loved the place.  It brought back his childhood and he kept pulling products off the shelves!  He also loved his sandwich and the specialty sausages he brought home.  Go here...go here NOW!!! 😎
